Corporate Accounts Manager BSD - Mobilink - Islamabad
Islamabad
Hold at least a Bachelor’s degree in Business Administration.
Have at least 4 to 6 years related experience.
Generate business from existing and new customers as per assigned target.
Ensure revenue and retention as per assigned target.
Build relations and develop rapport with the top tier of the company.
Monitor accounts for outstanding invoices and follow up with account contact person for timely.
Prepare sales contract and get approval for the relevant department.
Promote new product and services to corporate customers.
Conduct monthly reconciliation of accounts and mobile numbers.
Analyze customers’ monthly usage and suggest package plan accordingly.
Follow up with all corporate customers to maintain good relations and make sure they have no service issues.
Troubleshoot technical issues.
Good relationship management and customer handling skills
Strong communication (written/verbal) skills
Sound negotiation skills
Strong product knowledge
